SDL Console - A quake-like drop-down console for SDL 1 & 2.
SDL2 port by CryptoÂ²

This repo has a port of SDL_console to SDL2. It will only work in 2D/renderer mode have not tested OpenGL in any way. Sorry no docs/examples have been updated as yet but it's not hard to figure out @ all.

The original version can be found at http://sdlconsole.sourceforge.net/

